OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain clearing south early in
OL,6,Fthe morning to leave a sunny day for
OL,7,Fmost. Winds falling light as the day
OL,8,Fprogresses so a pleasant afternoon to
OL,9,Fcome.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure building through this period,
OL,13,Fto give plenty of warm sunshine and
OL,14,Flight winds throughout. Perhaps a
OL,15,Flittle more in the way of cloud on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
